						               													<description>Discover words based on the different themes shown by illutrated cards, and the letter indicated. &amp;quot;[The game of &amp;quot;Baccalaur&amp;eacute;at&amp;quot;] in its special pocket format&amp;quot;, according to the front of the box.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game evolves on a special board where players put their individual marker, at the beginning of the game they put them at the top of it. A round goes like this : the youngest player starts with a new picture drawn randomly. The goal is for player on their turn, to find a word that begins with the letter indicated by his/her marker position. If the player succeeds to find a word, his/her marker is moved to the next position ; if not, it stays in place for the next round. Once everyone played his/her turn, a new round begins with a new picture, and so on.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player who reaches the last line of the board represented by stars wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There is a possibility to make the game harder for advanced players by flipping the cardboard : this will reveal more difficult letters to find a word that begins with.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
